Here is an example of how the function can be used:

```python
string = "The Quick Brown Fox Jumps Over The Lazy Dog"
capital_indexes(string) # returns [4, 10, 13, 16]
```

In this example, the function returns a list of indexes [4, 10, 13, 16], which correspond to the positions of the capital letters in the given string..
